Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:04.05,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a broken satellite!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:07.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Conan's logic is good medicine\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.45,0:00:11.09,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Today's a tearful conclusion!\NDepend on him for the case and feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:12.63,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.63,0:00:14.60,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:16.89,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:41.78,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sonoko, Ran, and I went out\Nskiing on our day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.78,0:01:47.25,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There, we met their old grade school teacher, Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-sensei{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:50.28,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and took up her invitation to stay at a lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:55.50,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That night, someone attacked Sonoko and Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-sensei{\r\be10}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:02:00.70,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and the overdue Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-sensei{\r\be10} was found strangled to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:08.24,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}On each of their hands was a "mi", "na", and "ko"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:14.05,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Upon seeing this, Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-sensei{\r\be10} holed himself up in his room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.65,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thanks to Dr. Agasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.82,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I learned there was a suicide at Haido Elementary three years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:22.76,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and that the name of the deceased student was Minako Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:23.99,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:38.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Upstairs?! Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:39.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.61,0:02:42.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:44.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:45.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.91,0:02:48.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:53.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Rope marks on his neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:57.16,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The murder weapon isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:03:00.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The upstairs windows don't open,\Nand there aren't any exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:02.86,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means it's in someone's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:11.21,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not here! Not here! Not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's not anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Which means the rope is still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:18.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...in the killer's possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.74,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}One of them has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:27.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure there's no murder weapon, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, look at his neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:37.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See how he has rope marks, just like Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:40.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I don't see any rope in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:44.43,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Minori Nakamura (27)\NHaido Elementary Health Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:44.43,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko Yonehara (30)\NHaido Elementary Teacher\N(Ran & Sonoko's former teacher)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.22,0:03:44.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean the killer\Nran off somewhere with the rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:47.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:51.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was by the staircase the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:54.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're still upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:59.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just checked all the upstairs rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:02.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but didn't find any suspicious people or rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:05.87,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuichi Sakai (29)\NHaido Elementary P.E. Teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You checked our bags?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:10.08,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi Mori (37)\NNewspaper Reporter
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:10.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. If what the runt says is true...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:18.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...then one of you is the killer and is still carrying the rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.11,0:04:21.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're not a suspect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:26.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get serious. This is my first time upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:32.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I were the killer, this brat would've seen me go downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:35.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, whoever has the rope is the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:38.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do some body searches...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:48.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb! There was no rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:52.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Never thought I'd get stripped down in this weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:57.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, is it true that Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} was murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:05:04.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A cell phone kept ringing in his room next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:09.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I opened his door to check, he was already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:13.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound turned out to be his phone's alarm clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:17.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it from my room across the hall, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:20.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I thought you had a downstairs room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but I moved upstairs after you broke my door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.44,0:05:31.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if neither of us is the killer, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.45,0:05:34.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...that leaves only Sakai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:40.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're done body-searching already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:42.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he find the rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:47.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he didn't! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.69,0:05:50.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. How about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:52.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:55.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there's only one possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:59.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat is lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:02.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the killer might still be inside the lodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:06.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Sonoko's still asleep downstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, let's hurry to her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:17.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I never left the staircase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:22.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}The killer is definitely one of those three!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:26.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But why?! Why won't the weapon turn up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.50,0:06:29.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. She's just sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:40.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! It's terrible! Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} was murdered in her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:45.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then the killer strangled me with rope, like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:53.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, somehow. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:56.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, I'm still a little dizzy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.73,0:06:59.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then get some more rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:02.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't strangled?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:06.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but I had my forehead bashed into the wall instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:13.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you're all right! I always looked up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:21.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just her! All the girls\Nin our class looked up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:24.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't overrate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.19,0:07:29.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a woman who can't do\Nanything for her students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:34.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even help you today when you were attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:37.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer's to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:42.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how the students covered for you three years ago, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:47.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the teacher for the girl\Nwho killed herself, Minako Mochizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:52.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the killer's goal is to avenge her death,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:55.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's not surprising you were attacked first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:57.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:04.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were in charge of the volleyball club she was in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.37,0:08:11.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, she was Nakamura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s favorite in the Health Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:14.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've stopped her from committing suicide, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:20.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like this murder mystery will continue yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:24.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Murder mystery?! Don't tell me someone's been killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can explain later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, it's dangerous to be split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's gather in the living room\Nand wait for the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Damn it! What the heck's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:43.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Think! There's gotta be a key to unlocking this mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Somewhere in this ski lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.98,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}String?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.98,0:08:57.55,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's a long strand of fishing line!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:09:00.49,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}There's a broken rubber band on the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:04.02,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Was this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:07.89,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}OK! I've figured out the ringing-doorbell trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:10.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That just leaves the murder weapon, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:12.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If I can just find that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:21.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's it! I've figured out the disappearing-weapon trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.91,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This means that person is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.48,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But how do I tell everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:32.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I can't use Sonoko as a detective; she barely knows what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:37.22,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And I can't use Ran! I can't fool her afterwards like I can Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:40.63,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}My best bet is to pretend I heard everything from Conan
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:45.10,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and then use my real voice to explain it over the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:49.67,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No! If I do that with him there,\Nit'll get into the paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:54.59,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shin'ichi Kudo Makes Dashing Entrance"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.67,0:09:55.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}If my name gets into the paper,\Nthey'll find out I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:59.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Those men in black who shrunk me with a pill!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:03.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! No wandering off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The doc's weird phone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.72,0:10:14.26,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait! He mentioned that my Voice-Altering Bow Tie can transmit to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.29,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:24.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Your phone's ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.07,0:10:25.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Ran! Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:29.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.21,0:10:33.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured out who killed the two teachers at that lodge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:39.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told me.\NNow, I need you to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain the truth to everyone in my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:45.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:50.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll say it over the phone,\Nso you just repeat it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:54.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You can tell everyone over the phone yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:56.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, OK. You don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:10:58.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the police when they get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:04.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.31,0:11:09.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just put this on my ear\Nand say what you say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the others, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:13.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:17.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna get the person who attacked Sonoko and Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.82,0:11:20.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and killed the two teachers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:24.25,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Thanks, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:32.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! You figured out who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Eh?!\N- Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.11,0:11:36.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and everything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:41.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident #1, in which Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and Sonoko were attacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:44.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident #2, in which the strangled Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:47.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was set by the door to ring the doorbell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:50.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Incident #3, in which the killer strangled Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} upstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:54.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and disappeared with the murder weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.46,0:11:59.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out the one behind these three incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:00.74,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And that that person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.74,0:12:02.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that that person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:10.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer is one of us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A high school girl playing detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, we'll hear you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:22.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, are you prepared for what happens if you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.49,0:12:26.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd naturally be hit with a libel suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:30.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I put it in the paper and you're wrong, you'll be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:31.80,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:34.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you're prepared for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:36.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:39.67,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't worry, Ran. I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.01,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.01,0:12:48.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. If you just trust me and say what I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the truth will be revealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.19,0:12:54.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, li'l lady?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:57.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can write it if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:13:03.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Daughter of Great Kogoro Mouri Solves Murder Case at Ski Lodge"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.53,0:13:04.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:06.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:08.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the doorbell rang during Incident #2,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.87,0:13:13.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone was here in the living room but you three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:17.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How could we have done that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:21.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that would seem impossible. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:25.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...with this fishing line and the rubber band at the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:28.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that problem is easily overcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:29.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A fishing line and rubber band?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:31.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The trick is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:34.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You tie the rubber band to one end of the line,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:37.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,wrap the line around the two pillars by the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:43.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then tie the other end to the rubber band while making a small loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:47.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you attach the rubber band to the stiff Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s neck,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:52.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,lean him toward the door,\Nand support his feet with snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:58.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, you measure the line\Nso he'll stop just before the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:02.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Given time, the rubber band will snap due to the cold
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:05.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the body will fall and ring the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:10.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fishing line would then blow away and vanish from the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:19.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the killer murdered Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} hours before so he'd be stiff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:25.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer most likely called him out here and killed him
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:27.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,before we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:32.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw icicles when we arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Icicles?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:38.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Icicles couldn't have formed unless someone had been using the heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:44.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an interesting trick,\Nbut would it really work that well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:52.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Proof over theory! Go see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A ski I set up, using the same trick as I just explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.85,0:15:11.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the mystery behind Incident #3 has yet to be solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain that back in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! You're so cool, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:22.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait! I'm about to beat your attacker hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:30.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, li'l lady. If one of us is the killer, then let's hear about
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:37.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the mysterious trick used to make the rope disappear from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mysterious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:44.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer never intended to make it vanish to scare us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:50.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It only looked that way because Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} happened to be by the stairs
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:53.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,when the murder occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Had he not been there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:59.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we would've thought the killer had fled downstairs with the weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:05.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing them to escape suspicion as they were still upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.35,0:16:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they set the phone off and had the body found right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.35,0:16:14.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were discovered late,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:18.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,their clever trick to get rid of the weapon would've been in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:24.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the killer was one of us three upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:29.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then explain this weapon-disappearing trick already...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:33.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The rope wasn't in any of the upstairs rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.14,0:16:36.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.48,0:16:39.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's still in the killer's possession!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:45.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! We searched all three of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But not for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:50.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:52.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The one who murdered Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.40,0:16:58.53,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:04.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and attacked Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and Sonoko was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.57,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:07.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:13.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:18.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:22.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you, Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:26.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:27.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:34.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She braided her hair like a rope and strangled Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:37.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,as if it was real rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:44.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as long as her hair is,\Nshe couldn't just strangle people with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What if it was a wig?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.65,0:17:48.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A wig?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:52.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This was wrapped around Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hair from a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:58.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Its cuticle has been removed for easy processing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.19,0:18:00.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can tell just by touching...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:06.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, with her long hair, she's the only one capable of this trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:14.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be! I saw her lying right there when I was being strangled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:18.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:22.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. During Incident #1,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:29.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she dressed up his body, which she hid under her bed, just like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After luring Sonoko from the next room over,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,attacking from behind, and knocking her out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:41.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she hid the body under the bed again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:44.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and lied down in the same spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:47.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After making tracks in the snow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:51.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so we'd think the attacker ran out the window, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:56.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, she would look like a victim of the attacker,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:01.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,making it easier to get near Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, her next target...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:09.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yonehara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} most likely called him on his cell phone and said this:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:13.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I know who did it. Let me in and I'll tell you."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:20.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a great detective's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:24.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, this is a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:29.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I only wore it to hide my hair after I cut it too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:31.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.55,0:19:38.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still proof in your wig\Nthat you're the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:39.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:47.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? There were scratch marks on Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}'s neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:51.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, there should be some on that wig...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood that matches his scratches' perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:20:01.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your motive was likely the "Minako" written on the victims' hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:03.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To avenge my student murdered three years ago, Minako Mochizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.16,0:20:13.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Murdered?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.26,0:20:17.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time three years ago, she came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:22.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said two teachers were helping kids cheat on entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:29.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me one was Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}, but she didn't name the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:31.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was shocked it was one she looked up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so she was going to ask them herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.45,0:20:40.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The next day, she hanged herself in the volleyball room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:43.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I knew Sugiyama{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:47.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,had killed her to keep her quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:53.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I gathered teachers she liked\Nand planned this ski tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:58.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You all know the result. I quickly learned it was Shimoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you didn't have to kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:05.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As fellow teachers, they had to pay for betraying and killing a student
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.31,0:21:09.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who had looked up to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.22,0:21:12.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, who am I to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:17.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I troubled Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for my own trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:22.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for being such a horrible teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:50.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
